title: Father Gilbert Mysteries - The Play's The Thing
description: In The Play&#039;s The Thing, it&#039;s time for the 500th anniversary of the Stonebridge Faire - an event with a long history of mayhem and a legendary "curse." As part of the festivities, the Elsinore Players come to perform their new Shakespearean thriller. But "accidents" of a suspicious nature begin to happen. Is it a saboteur, or is something more sinister taking place?
